    provider: aws_bedrock
    model: us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0
}\if{html}{\out{</div>}}

With aliases, you can select a client by name in the interactive menu or pass
the alias directly: \code{btw_client(client = "sonnet")}.
}
